annotations.example: A list of annotations keyed by name (optional).
annotations.artifacthub.io/changes:
- kind: added
  description: Cool feature
  links:
    - name: Github Issue
      url: https://github.com/issue-url
    - name: Github PR
      url: https://github.com/pr-url
- kind: fixed
  description: Minor bug
  links:
    - name: Github Issue
      url: https://github.com/issue-url
annotations.artifacthub.io/images:
- name: img1
  image: repo/img1:1.0.0
- name: img2
  image: repo/img2:2.0.0
  whitelisted: true
annotations.artifacthub.io/crds:
- kind: MyKind
  version: v1
  name: mykind
  displayName: My Kind
  description: Some nice description
annotations.artifacthub.io/crdsExamples:
- apiVersion: v1
  kind: MyKind
  metadata:
    name: mykind
  spec:
    replicas: 1
annotations.artifacthub.io/links:
- name: link1
  url: https://link1.url
- name: link2
  url: https://link2.url
annotations.artifacthub.io/maintainers:
- name: user1
  email: user1@email.com
- name: user2
  email: user2@email.com
